{
  "_comment": "Order matters: first high-confidence match wins. Override per-user by copying to ~/.claude/skill-routing-manifest.json or via SKILL_ROUTER_MANIFEST_OVERRIDE. Inline files resolve relative to ${CLAUDE_PLUGIN_ROOT}; absolute and ~ paths are honoured as user overrides.",
